<div class="section">

<h3>PART VIII — Phylogenetic Inference using RAxML-NG</h3>

<pre>
!raxml-ng \
--msa clear_aligned_trimmed_kinesin.fasta \
--model LG+I+G4 \
--prefix KINESIN_TREE \
--threads 2
</pre>

<p>
RAxML-NG constructed the phylogenetic tree using maximum likelihood methods.
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">

<h3>PART IX — Bootstrap Analysis</h3>

<pre>
!raxml-ng \
--bootstrap \
--msa KINESIN_TREE.raxml.rba \
--model LG+I+G4 \
--prefix BOOTSTRAP \
--threads 2 \
--bs-tree 100
</pre>

<p>
Bootstrap analysis evaluated the statistical reliability of phylogenetic clades.
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">

<h3>PART X — Ancestral Sequence Reconstruction</h3>

<pre>
!raxml-ng \
--ancestral \
--msa clear_aligned_trimmed_kinesin.fasta \
--tree KINESIN_TREE.raxml.bestTree \
--model LG+I+G4 \
--prefix ASR
</pre>

<p>
Ancestral sequence reconstruction estimated probable ancestral kinesin protein sequences.
